---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
title="CassandraConsistentHashing&GossipProtocol"
description="InteractivevisualizationofCassandra'sconsistenthashingring,virtualnodes,gossipprotocol,replicationstrategies,andread/writepaths"
breadcrumbs={[
{label:"Home",href:"/"},
{label:"Cassandra",href:"/cassandra/"},
{label:"ConsistentHashing",href:"/cassandra/consistent-hashing/"}
]}
>
<div class="viz-container">
<header class="viz-header">
<h1>🟠ConsistentHashing&GossipProtocol</h1>
<p class="subtitle">HowCassandraDistributesDataandDiscoversClusterState</p>
</header>

<!--Overview-->
<section class="overview-section">
<div class="overview-card">
<p>
Cassandrausesa<strong>consistenthashingring</strong>todistributedataacrossnodes.The
<em>Murmur3Partitioner</em>hasheseachpartitionkeytoatokenintherange<strong>-2<sup>63</sup>to2<sup>63</sup>-1</strong>.
Eachnodeownstokenrangesonthering—with<em>virtualnodes(vnodes)</em>,asinglephysicalnode
ownsmanysmallranges(default256)forbetterbalance.Nodesdiscovereachotherandpropagate
statethrougha<strong>gossipprotocol</strong>,exchanginginfoeverysecond.The
<em>PhiAccrualFailureDetector</em>providesprobabilistic(notbinary)failuredetection.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<!--TokenRingVisualization-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>💍TokenRing</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Theconsistenthashingringwithnodes.Typeakeytoseewhereitlands.Togglevnodestoseedistributionchange.</p>

<div class="flow-controls">
<div class="slider-group">
<label>Nodes:<strong id="nodeCountLabel">6</strong></label>
<input type="range" id="nodeSlider" min="3" max="12" value="6" class="slot-slider">
</div>
<label class="toggle-label">
<input type="checkbox" id="vnodeToggle">
<span class="toggle-switch"></span>
<span>Vnodes(256pernode)</span>
</label>
<button id="applyRingBtn" class="action-btnprimary-btn">🔄Apply</button>
</div>

<div class="calculator-container">
<div class="calc-input-row">
<input type="text" id="keyInput" placeholder="Typeapartitionkey(e.g.user:1001)" class="key-input" autocomplete="off">
<button id="calcBtn" class="action-btnprimary-btn">Hash</button>
</div>
<div class="calc-result" id="calcResult"></div>
<div class="calc-formula" id="calcFormula"></div>
</div>

<div class="topology-container">
<canvas id="ringCanvas" width="820" height="500"></canvas>
</div>
<div class="node-legend" id="nodeLegend"></div>
</section>

<!--Replication-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>📋Replication</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Setareplicationfactorandseehowreplicasareplacedonthering.Togglebetweenstrategies.</p>

<div class="flow-controls">
<div class="slider-group">
<label>RF:<strong id="rfLabel">3</strong></label>
<input type="range" id="rfSlider" min="1" max="5" value="3" class="slot-slider">
</div>
<select id="strategySelect" class="select-input">
<optionvalue="simple">SimpleStrategy</option>
<optionvalue="network">NetworkTopologyStrategy</option>
</select>
<button id="applyReplicationBtn" class="action-btnprimary-btn">Apply</button>
</div>

<div class="topology-container">
<canvas id="replicationCanvas" width="820" height="500"></canvas>
</div>

<div class="replication-info" id="replicationInfo"></div>
</section>

<!--ReplicationExplainer-->
<section class="explain-section">
<div class="explain-grid">
<div class="explain-card">
<h3>🔄SimpleStrategy</h3>
<p>
Walk<strong>clockwise</strong>fromthetokenonthering.Placereplicasonthenext
<em>Ndistinctnodes</em>(whereN=replicationfactor).Simple,butdoesn'tconsider
rackordatacenterplacement.Fineforsingle-DCdeployments.
</p>
</div>
<div class="explain-card">
<h3>🌐NetworkTopologyStrategy</h3>
<p>
Walksclockwisebutensuresreplicaslandon<strong>differentracks</strong>withineachDC.
YousetRFperdatacenter(e.g.,<code>DC1:3,DC2:2</code>).Thisisthe<em>productionstandard</em>—
survivesrackfailuresanddatacenteroutages.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!--GossipProtocol-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>📡GossipProtocol</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Watchgossippropagatea"nodedown"event.Eachround,nodespick1-3randompeerstogossipwith.</p>

<div class="flow-controls">
<button id="startGossipBtn" class="action-btnkill-btn">💀MarkNodeDown</button>
<button id="stepGossipBtn" class="action-btnstep-btn"disabled>⏭GossipRound</button>
<button id="autoGossipBtn" class="action-btnauto-btn"disabled>⚡Auto-Play</button>
<button id="resetGossipBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn">🔄Reset</button>
</div>

<div class="flow-status" id="gossipStatus">
<span class="status-badgeidle" id="gossipBadge">Ready</span>
<span class="status-text" id="gossipStatusText">Click"MarkNodeDown"tobegingossippropagation</span>
</div>

<div class="topology-container">
<canvas id="gossipCanvas" width="820" height="400"></canvas>
</div>

<div class="gossip-stats" id="gossipStats"></div>
<div class="failover-timeline" id="gossipTimeline"></div>
</section>

<!--PhiAccrualFailureDetector-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>📈PhiAccrualFailureDetector</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Unlikebinary"alive/dead",Cassandrausesasuspicionlevel(φ)thatincreasesovertimewithoutheartbeats</p>

<div class="flow-controls">
<button id="startPhiBtn" class="action-btnprimary-btn">▶Simulate</button>
<button id="resetPhiBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn">🔄Reset</button>
</div>

<div class="topology-container">
<canvas id="phiCanvas" width="820" height="300"></canvas>
</div>

<div class="phi-info" id="phiInfo"></div>
</section>

<!--PhiExplainer-->
<section class="explain-section">
<div class="explain-cardhighlight-card">
<h3>💡WhyPhiAccrual?</h3>
<p>
Traditionalfailuredetectorsarebinary:anodeiseitheraliveordeadafterafixedtimeout.
The<strong>PhiAccrualFailureDetector</strong>outputsa<em>suspicionlevel</em>(φ)basedonthe
statisticaldistributionofinter-arrivaltimesofheartbeats.Aφof<strong>1</strong>means~10%
chancethenodeisdown;φof<strong>8</strong>(Cassandra'sdefaultthreshold)means99.999997%
likelydown.Thisadaptsautomaticallytonetworkconditions—nomanualtimeouttuningneeded.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<!--Read/WritePath-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>📨Read&WritePath</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Seewhichnodesparticipatebasedonconsistencylevel.Thecoordinatordeterminesreplicasfromthetokenring.</p>

<div class="flow-controls">
<select id="clSelect" class="select-input">
<optionvalue="ONE">ONE</option>
<optionvalue="QUORUM"selected>QUORUM</option>
<optionvalue="ALL">ALL</option>
<optionvalue="LOCAL_QUORUM">LOCAL_QUORUM</option>
</select>
<button id="writeBtn" class="action-btnprimary-btn">✍Write</button>
<button id="readBtn" class="action-btnstep-btn">📖Read</button>
<button id="resetRwBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn">🔄Reset</button>
</div>

<div class="flow-status" id="rwStatus">
<span class="status-badgeidle" id="rwBadge">Ready</span>
<span class="status-text" id="rwStatusText">PickaconsistencylevelandclickWriteorRead</span>
</div>

<div class="topology-container">
<canvas id="rwCanvas" width="820" height="420"></canvas>
</div>

<div class="failover-timeline" id="rwTimeline"></div>
</section>

<!--CLExplainer-->
<section class="explain-section">
<div class="explain-grid">
<div class="explain-card">
<h3>✍WritePath</h3>
<p>
Thecoordinatorsendsthewriteto<strong>allreplicanodes</strong>,butonlywaitsfor
<em>CL</em>acknowledgmentsbeforerespondingtotheclient.With<code>QUORUM</code>andRF=3,
thecoordinatorwaitsfor<strong>2of3</strong>replicas.Eachreplicawritestothe
<strong>commitlog</strong>and<strong>memtable</strong>—acknowledgedassoonasbothsucceed.
</p>
</div>
<div class="explain-card">
<h3>📖ReadPath</h3>
<p>
Thecoordinatorreadsfrom<em>CL</em>replicas:onegetsa<strong>fulldatarequest</strong>,
othersget<strong>digestrequests</strong>(hashonly).Ifdigestsdon'tmatch,a
<em>readrepair</em>istriggered—thecoordinatorfetchesfulldatafromallreplicas,
picksthelatesttimestamp,andpushesthecorrectversiontostalereplicas.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<!--Adding/RemovingNodes-->
<section class="flow-section">
<h2>🔧Adding&RemovingNodes</h2>
<p class="section-desc">Watchtokenrangesrebalancewhennodesjoinorleavethecluster</p>

<div class="flow-controls">
<button id="addNodeBtn" class="action-btnprimary-btn">➕AddNode</button>
<button id="removeNodeBtn" class="action-btnkill-btn">➖RemoveNode</button>
<button id="resetNodesBtn" class="action-btnreset-btn">🔄Reset</button>
</div>

<div class="flow-status" id="nodeOpStatus">
<span class="status-badgeidle" id="nodeOpBadge">Ready</span>
<span class="status-text" id="nodeOpStatusText">Addorremovenodestoseedatastreaming</span>
</div>

<div class="topology-container">
<canvas id="nodeOpCanvas" width="820" height="500"></canvas>
</div>

<div class="failover-timeline" id="nodeOpTimeline"></div>
</section>

<footer class="viz-footer">
<p>Basedon<ahref="https://cassandra.apache.org/doc/latest/cassandra/architecture/" target="_blank">ApacheCassandraDocumentation</a>and<ahref="https://www.datastax.com/blog/how-cassandra-distributes-data" target="_blank">DataStaxArchitectureGuides</a></p>
</footer>

<div class="share-buttons">
<span>Sharethisvisualization:</span>
<ahref="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Interactive%20visualization%20of%20Cassandra%20consistent%20hashing%20and%20gossip%20protocol&url=https://systeminternals.dev/cassandra/consistent-hashing/" target="_blank" class="share-btn">𝕏Twitter</a>
<ahref="https://www.linkedin.com/sharing/share-offsite/?url=https://systeminternals.dev/cassandra/consistent-hashing/" target="_blank" class="share-btn">inLinkedIn</a>
<ahref="https://news.ycombinator.com/submitlink?u=https://systeminternals.dev/cassandra/consistent-hashing/&t=Interactive%20Cassandra%20Consistent%20Hashing%20%26%20Gossip%20Protocol%20Visualizer" target="_blank" class="share-btn">🟧HackerNews</a>
</div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>

